Engine Responsibilities (Given This DSL)

For any valid DSL spec, the Simulated Replicator must:

- Parse all blocks into internal objects  
- Build a feasible design space under CONSTRAINTS + POLICY  
- Generate candidate recipes via RecipeEngine  
- Simulate composition, nutrition, and sensory estimates  
- Enforce hard constraints, optimize soft preferences  
- Output:
  - final recipe graph  
  - ingredient list  
  - process steps  
  - justification (which constraints/prefs drove which choices)  
